      "title": "Donald Trump : the dirtiest person in the world",
      "slug": "donald-trump-the-dirtiest-person-in-the-world",
      "excerpt": "",
      "content": "The characterization of Donald Trump as the \"dirtiest person in the world\" is an opinionated statement, not a objective fact, and is typically used in a figurative sense to describe perceived moral, ethical, or political corruption. Various sources, including political analysts, former associates, and media outlets, have used such language or similar strong terms when discussing his actions, character, and business practices.",
