  {
    "model": "blog.post",
    "pk": 5,
    "fields": {
      "title": "Believe in Yourself",
      "slug": "believe-in-yourself",
      "excerpt": "",
      "content": "Who am I? What is my identity? What can I do and what can I not do? Finding answers to these questions builds true confidence. When a person understands their strengths and weaknesses, they can move forward successfully. Real identity comes from believing in yourself, not from othersďż˝ opinions. Confidence gives people courage to dream, learn, and achieve great things in life.",
